{"tid":2317922,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"江嘉敏瞞男友「偷食」新聞翻hit 不忿被翻舊賬：唔該唔好消費我","createTime":"2020-12-09T03:08:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-09T17:13:03.000Z","uid":212249,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8bee8f4765283813a51952847b283f88eba9992e","tid":2317922,"uid":212249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T03:08:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/YeKrbFGJGaGqe_Veg-QHKgnHKrA=/720x405/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/MLUZMT3WJNGCHKM5LUEN7RJNOY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FYeKrbFGJGaGqe_Veg-QHKgnHKrA%3D%2F720x405%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FMLUZMT3WJNGCHKM5LUEN7RJNOY.jpg&h=e8442783&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n江嘉敏入行短短日子，是非、緋聞加加埋埋10隻手指數唔晒，當中包括扭計被大台掟入雪櫃，拍劇時又先後和余德丞、何廣沛和王浩信等人傳過緋聞，早前又因上富豪船P和好姊妹馮盈盈反目。被指拜金的江嘉敏，現時已成功和小小超女友郭嘉文埋堆一齊玩，向上流社會邁進一大步。<br />\n<br />\n相比以上是非，以下一單的花生味更濃。去年9月，《壹週刊》報道江嘉敏瞞着電競公司高層男友Anthony繼續收兵，疑暗媾男友的朋友兼生意拍檔X先生，二人的WhatsApp截圖更被流出。江嘉敏除叫對方以50萬打本給她做生意開琴行外，又指二人夾計隱瞞Anthony，以公幹為理由齊齊飛去日本「偷食」。由於近日這段新聞再度在YouTube上架，結果看過的人再次重溫，未看過的人又互相轉載，成為茶餘飯後話題，結果成功令這單新聞翻hit。而當事人江嘉敏估計受這件事影響心情，昨日在IG動態上疑似不忿被人翻舊賬說：「事實真相已經有好多好好嘅報紙同記者幫我澄清咗！唔該唔好再消費我！多謝。」<br />\n<br />\n去年這段新聞出街後，江嘉敏雖然承認被樂易玲照肺，但她亦抵唔住頸在IG出post反擊，更開名指X先生叫王仁灝，她直指對方將WhatsApp的訊息「cap頭cap尾」，又指這樣做絕不會影響她和男友感情。不過《壹週刊》之後再爆料，指江嘉敏趁王仁灝去日本、意大利等地方公幹時，Cap圖列出送禮清單，包括Hermes手鈪、拖鞋、粉底、100份日本手信等，還試探叫男方買一部價值80萬的七人車，被指貪婪之極。"},{"pid":"e9f4df43794ce4916a7a1d4741e8f82e24651f60","tid":2317922,"uid":212249,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T03:08:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201208/LYFVGAKX45GDZDXVIH6KTPTVZM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201208%2FLYFVGAKX45GDZDXVIH6KTPTVZM%2F&d=If5g8ybbdlMRYcYioqq3W%2FkXgXr6FxeO6pMo8RORPdo%3D&h=5e5d3986\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201208%2FLYFVGAKX45GDZDXVIH6KTPTVZM%2F&h=4a4c1580\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201208/LYFVGAKX45GDZDXVIH6KTPTVZM/</a>"},{"pid":"0d559c7fd4a5d268955454bae2fb527388809c5f","tid":2317922,"uid":136416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T03:09:38.000Z","msg":"等聽有人唱首歌"},{"pid":"4ab017bd92105c323fb318e14c92a68273f0570d","tid":2317922,"uid":261468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T03:24:44.000Z","msg":"呢幾日第一次睇，笑到癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b07104cec78aad3af9ee82f929afc77188d5567c","tid":2317922,"uid":383773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0d559c7fd4a5d268955454bae2fb527388809c5f","tid":2317922,"uid":136416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T03:09:38.000Z","msg":"等聽有人唱首歌"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T17:13:03.000Z","msg":"肛交敏就等於火 老加雞就等於我<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/rEyAiNX\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/rEyAiNX</a><br />\n#216 回覆 - 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}